'''Undervector''' were a [[Band/Legends|band]] whose [[Music/Legends|music]] was composed entirely of sounds from their home planet, and could also be made into a mathematical equation to define the output of a quantum vector. They became popular following the deaths of [[Palpatine/Legends|Palpatine]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] at the [[Battle of Endor/Legends|Battle of Endor]].

[[Dllr Nep]] disliked Undervector's music, claiming "they stink like [[Tauntaun/Legends|Tauntaun]] droppings".

